name: Farmers Markets,Kentucky, 2009
description: This dataset was created from the USDA Farmers Market database listing. The point data is usually the exact location of the market but may sometimes be the general area. Attributes include contact information, hours, and if the market takes food stamps. Address were geocoded using batchgeocode.com. Most points are not be the exact location.
